text: Anders Christensson (born 7 March 1973) is a Swedish rower. He competed in the men's lightweight double sculls event at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1973 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Sweden Category:Rowers at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:People from Ängelholm Municipality
